formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1)We have relied on financial statements provided by promoter of the project while issuing Form 3.
2)As per the act and regulation, it is mandatory to execute agreement for sale for the units before  receiving amount more than 10 % of the unit consideration amount and report date of AFS to GUJRERA. We hereby report that promoter has not followed above provisions for certain units. 
3)As per Form 3 it is required to report unit wise encumbrance status at the reporting date. We would like to state that we have relied on the representation received from Promoter while reporting unit wise status of encumbrance.
